==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Styrax
<hw>Sty"rax</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>styrax</ets>,
<ets>storax</ets>, Gr. <?/. See <er>Storax</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of shrubs and trees, mostly American or
Asiatic, abounding in resinous and aromatic substances. <spn>Styrax
officinalis</spn> yields storax, and <spn>Styrax Benzoin</spn> yields
benzoin.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Same as <er>Storax</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Styrol</ent>⟦br⟧
